6 C. The criteria for admission to a program or course at an
7 institution of higher education shall not have the effect of
8 restricting access by persons of a particular race, ethnicity,
9 national origin, sex, disability, religion, or marital status;
10 provided, this shall not infringe upon the rights of student faith-
